import React from 'react';
import { Container, Row, Col, Form, Button, Card, Pagination } from 'react-bootstrap';

const UserDashboard = () => {
  // Dummy data for cards
  const items = [
    { id: 1, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 2, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 3, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 4, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 5, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 6, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 7, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 8, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 9, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 10, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 11, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 12, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 13, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 14, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    { id: 15, name: 'Item 1', location: 'Near ABC', image: 'image_url_1.jpg' },
    { id: 16, name: 'Item 2', location: 'Near XYZ', image: 'image_url_2.jpg' },
    // ... More items
  ];

  return (
    <Container fluid>
      <Row>
        {/* Sidebar */}
        <Col md={3}>
          {/* Filter options */}
          {/* Add your filter options here */}
          <Form>
            {/* Example filter option */}
            <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
              <Form.Label>Filter Options</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control as="select">
                <option>Option 1</option>
                <option>Option 2</option>
                {/* Add more options */}
              </Form.Control>
            </Form.Group>
          </Form>
        </Col>

        {/* Item List */}
        <Col md={9}>
          {/* Search bar and Add Item button */}
          <Form className="mb-3">
            <Row>
              <Col md={8}>
                <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Search..." />
              </Col>
              <Col md={4} className="text-right">
                <Button variant="primary">Add Item</Button>
              </Col>
            </Row>
          </Form>

          {/* Display Cards */}
          <Row>
            {items.map(item => (
              <Col key={item.id} md={3} className="mb-3">
                <Card>
                  <Card.Img variant="top" src={item.image} />
                  <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>{item.name}</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>{`Lost/Found it ${item.location}`}</Card.Text>
                    <Button variant="primary">View Item</Button>
                  </Card.Body>
                </Card>
              </Col>
            ))}
          </Row>

          {/* Pagination */}
          <Row>
            <Col className="text-center">
              <Pagination>
                <Pagination.Prev />
                <Pagination.Item active>{1}</Pagination.Item>
                <Pagination.Item>{2}</Pagination.Item>
                <Pagination.Item>{3}</Pagination.Item>
                <Pagination.Next />
              </Pagination>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default UserDashboard;
